				<p><a href="http://www.antipixel.com/blog/archives/2002/10/22/steal_these_buttons.html#marc_garrett_002084" title="Permalink to this comment" class="noborder"><img src="/blog//images/permalink.gif" alt="" width="7" height="9" style="margin-right:8px;" /></a><a id="marc_garrett_002084"></a>Posted by <a title="http://since1968.com" href="http://since1968.com" rel="nofollow">Marc Garrett</a> &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="feint">2003.03.30, 13:21</span></p>
