		<div style="border-bottom:1px dotted #bbb; margin:0px 30px 15px 30px;"> </div>
				<p><a href="http://www.antipixel.com/blog/archives/2002/10/22/steal_these_buttons.html#jh_004352" title="Permalink to this comment" class="noborder"><img src="/blog//images/permalink.gif" alt="" width="7" height="9" style="margin-right:8px;" /></a><a id="jh_004352"></a>Posted by <a title="http://www.antipixel.com/" href="http://www.antipixel.com/" rel="nofollow">jh</a> &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="feint">2003.12.14, 09:55</span></p>
		<blockquote><p>The font is <a href="http://kottke.org/plus/type/silkscreen/index.html" title="Download Silkscreen here" rel="nofollow">Silkscreen</a> by Jason Kottke.</p>
</blockquote>
		<div style="border-bottom:1px dotted #bbb; margin:0px 30px 15px 30px;"> </div>
				<p><a href="http://www.antipixel.com/blog/archives/2002/10/22/steal_these_buttons.html#brad_knapp_004365" title="Permalink to this comment" class="noborder"><img src="/blog//images/permalink.gif" alt="" width="7" height="9" style="margin-right:8px;" /></a><a id="brad_knapp_004365"></a>Posted by <a title="http://www.bradknapp.com" href="http://www.bradknapp.com" rel="nofollow">brad knapp</a> &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="feint">2003.12.17, 07:59</span></p>
		<blockquote><p>I took your little button and slightly modified ti so that people that didn&#8217;t yet know what RSS is might get their interest piqued. Check it out at  <a href="http://www.braadknapp.com " rel="nofollow">my little photoblog</a>  lower right column</p>
</blockquote>
		<div style="border-bottom:1px dotted #bbb; margin:0px 30px 15px 30px;"> </div>
